Minimum Level: 65<br>
Zone Name: Plane of Fire<br>
Camp Area/LOC: Zone in<br>
Mob List (HP): Mephits, Flame Lords, Spiders, Horses (24-28k)<br>
Availability (1-&gt;10): 9<br>
Loot Ranking (1-&gt;10): 7<br>
Diff.Ranking (1-&gt;10): 7<br>
Faction Affected: none<br>
<br>
Other Notes/Tips/Warnings: All of the zone in mobs run at basically the same speed. Some mobs are randomly immune to snare so the best tactic is to kite them full speed. You can run them through the valley directly behind the zone in, no fear of adds as nothing pathes there. They only drop trade skill items, but some of the items sell for some really good pp. Expect 5-6% AA per mob. If you have been in the elementals for a while and you have good mana regen you can octakite pretty easily. Watch out for the named that spawn in the ZI area, they are red to 65 and they will summon you for a beatdown. The named are loot/rune droppers and can be killed with one group. <p><div align="center" class="font-size: 11px; font-family: arial">
