<br>
It's about EXP/hour not per quad.  At 51 your mana to damage ratio on a quad goes up to almost 10 to 1 so your able to kill twice as many birds for less mana.<br>
<br>
Judging by my manapool, I was getting about 4.5% for 2 quads depending on how many lt blues happened to spawn.<br>
<br>
----<br>
<br>
At 52 I could divide the city in half and take out all the roamers and static spawns on the east beach with only 1 med break.  By end of second med break (no spiroks anywhere) they'd start repoping for me.  <br>
<br>
Exp was still equal to CS, in my opinion, but CS has WAY better loot. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lemni>Lemni</A> at: 6/7/03 6:43 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ssake>Ssake</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/14/03 12:58 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: breaking large island spawn</span><hr size=1> Bump <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=destinyysz>Destinyy SZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/24/03 4:56 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spirocs 34-52</span><hr size=1>      I did Spirocs from 34-52.  Had KEI and SOW for all of it. <br>
wasn't until ~40 till I had mana left over (mostly due to snare + CoF resists). I got ~12%+ xp per quad at 34, 3% at 50.  I wanted to kill myself after the 18 levels doing the same camp and 51 was kinda slow (did some at raptors).<br>
     Constant PvP fights over the camp on Sullon Zek tho, kept it interesting. Did it in less than a week, mad xp, and the loots even better when you kill a druid thats been kiting them for a bit. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
