Minimum Level: 52 is when I started, might be possible earlier<br>
Maximum Level: 55 (when you hit 55 most of them should turn light blue to you or even green)<br>
Zone Name: Dawnshroud Peaks<br>
Camp Area/LOC: Rockhopper Cave<br>
Mob List (HP): Various Rockhoppers<br>
Availability (1-&gt;10): 8 (usually very good. Fast repop so even with three groups around you should be able to pull without waiting)<br>
Loot Ranking (1-&gt;10): 5 (crappy loot, but superb and flawless hides are worth around 150 to 300pp to tailors)<br>
Diff.Ranking (1-&gt;10): 3 (very easy, round up on the hill that goes off at a right angle from the cave and then kite towards ME on the hill side. Beware of wolf adds and don't run into the shrooms, that's all.)<br>
Faction Affected: Dawnshroud Hoppers down and the Red guys up.<br>
<br>
One more thing: Pull by going into the cave invis. Count your hoppers and then click the last one running by the others and aggroing them that way.<br>
And don't try to quad kite the red guys. They have shamans who sow themselves and those around.<br>
<br>
Ceres Whirlwind<br>
Lvl 55 Wizard<br>
